Buzzer-beater finishes, major upsets, heated battles and huge maneuvers, Stop 1 of the Rip Curl #GromSearch presented by @banzaibowls did not disappoint 😳

Relive all the action from this past weekend, then hit our bio for the full event wrap up.

Next stop, Kewalos for our Hawaiian Qualifier on July 24-25!

A huge thank you to all our series sponsors for making this event possible: @banzaibowls, @flexfit, @gopro, @sunbum, @lostsurfboards, @fcs_surf, @softech_softboards, @wahoosfishtaco!
